For those of you who don't know, our dear friend Zac has recently been diagnosed with a rare autoimmune disease. While this disease is treatable, Zac's insurance will no longer cover his treatment, and the expenses are substantial ($26000). This illness has rendered Zac unable to use his hands (or tattoo), which means he has lost his source of income and is now in a challenging situation.

He's a talented tattoo artist, musician, skateboarder, snowboarder, and dirtbike enthusiast, but he can't enjoy any of the things he loves. I understand that this raffle won't cure his disease, but it can hopefully alleviate some of the financial burdens he's facing. Any form of donation is greatly appreciated. Let's all do our best to raise as much money as possible for Zac and help him regain a normal life. 💕 Please refer to the second slide for instructions. 🙏🏼 
@zac_siravo
